    "updated_at": "2019-08-04T18:15:52Z",
    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Id like to add, there should be 2 unique paths so we don't confuse them. The paths don't overlap.\r\n\r\n1.)\r\nreceive attestation **->** attestation gets put into pool **->** attestations get packaged into a block **->** block gets passed to the proposer **->** proposer signs and submits it back\r\n⬆️ This is for fork choice and block produce\r\n\r\n2.)\r\nreceive block **->** process attestations in the block and verify they are valid, if not, discard the block\r\n⬆️ This is for finality gadget and rewards/penalties",
